  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 268bf36e2c95048f4b4ca0fcdf827688, type: 3}
  m_Name: BeginningData
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  SpeakerName: Dialogue
  lines:
  - Welcome to your first day on the job!
  - In order for you to have the smoothest shift, let's run down the basis.
  - Press the WASD Keys to move around.
  - You need to be able to see where you going, the Mouse will do that for you.
  - If you ever feel lost, press P!
  - 'I updated this call to your log, you can see all the important information. '
  - For now, there's a resident in need of your assistance.
  - Meet him at the first floor.
